text: Two Suicide Attempts in Six Weeks  How Did I Get Here  and Why Am I Still Here  In the past six weeks  I ve made two serious attempts at suicide  Last month  I very clumsily attempted to drown myself in my neighborhood pool  Today  I strangled myself with an electronic charging cord I feel like such a fucking failure  It s like I have the reverse Midas Touch  Everything I approach turns to shit  What s wrong with me  Why am I always failing Was I set up for failure at the very beginning  or am I just doing everything wrong because I don t know how to make it right  Either way  does it even really matter  Whatever the case  I m such a fucking failure and I don t know how to fix it It often seems like even the smallest things can now drive me over the edge and cause me to completely fly off the rails  This time  me going   days without being paid at work  Other times  it s been me losing my phone for a few minutes   But throughout my life  I ve survived multiple traumatic experiences  My birth mother subjected me to coercive control abuse as a child  I struck out several times in my romantic love life as a young adult  And more recently  I had a  stable office job  that was ultimately anything but stable   Still  I wonder what I could have done to overcome these challenges  Other people have endured much worse and emerged as better people  Why can t I do more than just survive  Why am I always sinking to rock bottom I don t know whether I m writing this as a cry for help  or as a preview of my last will and testament  Only time will tell  I just figured I had to write something down  Maybe one day  someone will find my Reddit account and realize just how terrifying my life has been behind the veneer of tranquility I ve carefully constructed to hide all this   Right now  I feel so awkward  I should be grateful I m still alive  I should be hopeful that my work pay SNAFU was found and may soon be solved  Instead  I just feel guilty  Why can t I escape this abyss I ve fallen into
summary: In the past six weeks, I have made two serious attempts at suicide. Today I strangled myself with an electronic charging cord. I feel like such a failure. Even the smallest things can drive me over the edge and cause me to fly off the rails. I have survived multiple traumatic experiences in my life.
